          <p>MR. HAROLD THERAULT: Madam Speaker, I'm pleased to stand and speak a little bit on Bill No. 124. We fully support this bill and we're looking forward to it to go to Law Amendments Committee and, hopefully, be proclaimed as quickly as possible.</p>
        </speech>
        <speech by="#75109949-5b99-4b9c-b9fd-d85a8ce227ab">
