          <from>MR. KEITH BAIN</from>
          <p>MR. KEITH BAIN : Thank you, Madam Speaker, and I thank the member for Digby-Annapolis for mentioning us during debate on this bill.</p>
        </speech>
        <speech by="#75109949-5b99-4b9c-b9fd-d85a8ce227ab">
