        </speech>
        <speech by="#75109949-5b99-4b9c-b9fd-d85a8ce227ab">
          <from>MADAM SPEAKER</from>
          <p>MADAM SPEAKER : Order, please. The chatter in the room is getting a little loud. The honourable member for Truro-Bible Hill has the floor.</p>
